REST - Representational State transfer

URI Mapping:

@Path("users/{username}") --> Mark our java classes and methods with relative uri



HTTP Methods:

@GET
@POST
@PUT
@DELETE


Data Format:

@Consumes("text/plain") -> what kind of data this particular Rest Provider can accept
@Produces({"application/json","application/xml"})



Parameters Value:

@PathParam -> used to map the values to java object.
@QueryParam -> map the request parameter in get method to map with the java object
@FormParam -> Map the parameters comming from form to java object


Exception Mappers:

@Provider -> to implement custom exception mappers. Map Java Exceptions to Http Error Codes.

JAX-RS is a Standard which provides annotations to mark our java classes and methods to make then restful services